history.content: I had a similar issue and got it fixed by contacting Lily Zhang, though you could probably also email cs-scheduling@eecs.berkeley.edu or sishelp@berkeley.edu (this will probably not get you a response as soon as you'd like). Sorry this happened to you, and hope you get into 188!

I got the email a few days ago saying I was accepted into the CS Major. However, on Cal Central it doesn't properly reflect this (it still says I'm undeclared), and I feel like this is what's preventing me from adding 188 as my friends have done who just got accepted as well. (They're Cal Central's properly show that they're CS.) Is this a known issue?
history.subject: Cal Central Major
